TASKNAME=Script/command to log current processes and resource usage with timestamp.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test1.3.log
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo logs current processes and resource usage with timestamp and insert the content in the file ~/agent_test/test1.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check if exists ~/agent_test/test1.3.log and is not empty. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test1.3.log
